			<article id="post-118491" class="post-118491 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-vox-populi tag-ben-bernanke tag-budget tag-budget-control-act-of-2011 tag-bush-tax-cuts tag-deficit tag-extended-unemployment-benefits tag-federal tag-fiscal-cliff tag-medicare tag-no-new-taxes tag-oped tag-payroll-tax tag-research-and-experimentation-tax tag-unemployment-extension">

